Hi,
You can try using dietlibc (
http://www.fefe.de/dietlibc/
) and other
tools listed on 
http://www.fefe.de/
 . There is also a project rewriting
shell tools in assembler but I do not remember the name. This should
reduce required root space a little.
cheers Esden
